OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1780729501
OL,3,C'Seven years stolen': Father
OL,4,Cmisdiagnosed with terminal cancer
OL,6,FWatch Mark Gough's report on Simon
OL,7,FPearson's cancer misdiagnosis after
OL,8,Fyears of hospital treatment
OL,10,FA father who spent seven years
OL,11,Fbelieving he had terminal cancer has
OL,12,Ftold ITV News of the moment he
OL,13,Fdiscovered he had been misdiagnosed
OL,14,Fall along.
OL,16,FSimon Pearson, from Tamworth, told ITV
OL,17,Fhe "cried for 10 minutes" after
OL,18,Flearning he never had the blood cancer
OL,19,Fdoctors told him he was living with.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
