FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1780729501
OL,3,C'Seven years stolen': Father
OL,4,Cmisdiagnosed with terminal cancer
OL,6,FThe father-of-two underwent years of
OL,7,Fhospital treatment, including more
OL,8,Fthan 40 procedures to remove blood
OL,9,Ffrom his body, after being wrongly
OL,10,Fdiagnosed with a rare blood cancer and
OL,11,Fa separate genetic condition.
OL,13,FSpeaking to ITV, Mr Pearson said
OL,14,Fdiscovering the diagnosis was wrong
OL,15,Fleft him struggling to process what
OL,16,Fhad happened.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1780729501
OL,3,C'Seven years stolen': Father
OL,4,Cmisdiagnosed with terminal cancer
OL,6,F"I walked out and literally just rang
OL,7,Fmy wife. I said, 'I've got good news',
OL,8,Fbut then cried for 10 minutes on the
OL,9,Fphone - and I just couldn't get my
OL,10,Fhead round it," he said.
OL,12,F"It's just something that you think,
OL,13,Fwell, hang on a minute."
OL,15,FMr Pearson, now 41, was referred to
OL,16,Fthe haematology department at George
OL,17,FEliot Hospital in Nuneaton in 2017
OL,18,Fafter experiencing tiredness, a high
OL,19,Fred blood cell count and abnormal iron
OL,20,Flevels.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1780729501
OL,3,C'Seven years stolen': Father
OL,4,Cmisdiagnosed with terminal cancer
OL,6,FHe was diagnosed with polycythaemia
OL,7,Fvera, a chronic blood cancer he says
OL,8,Fhe was told was terminal, and later
OL,9,Fwith haemochromatosis, a genetic
OL,10,Fcondition that can cause toxic iron
OL,11,Fbuild-up and organ damage.
OL,13,FThe diagnoses had a profound impact on
OL,14,Fhis life and family.
OL,16,FAsked whether the seven years had
OL,17,Feffectively been stolen from him, he
OL,18,Ftold ITV News: "Well, yes, because
OL,19,Fyou're kind of thinking, well I can't
OL,20,Fgo and do that because I've got a
OL,21,Fprocedure to have.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1780729501
OL,3,C'Seven years stolen': Father
OL,4,Cmisdiagnosed with terminal cancer
OL,6,F"So for two or three days after that
OL,7,FI'm not going to be feeling great, so
OL,8,Fyou do kind of put things on the back-
OL,9,Fburner."
OL,11,FMr Pearson also had to live with the
OL,12,Ffear he could have passed the
OL,13,Fcondition on to his two sons.
OL,15,FIt was not until a routine appointment
OL,16,Fin June 2025 that a nurse raised
OL,17,Fconcerns about his diagnosis. Further
OL,18,Finvestigations found he did not have
OL,19,Feither of the conditions he had been
OL,20,Ftreated for.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1780729501
OL,3,C'Seven years stolen': Father
OL,4,Cmisdiagnosed with terminal cancer
OL,6,FA subsequent patient safety
OL,7,Finvestigation concluded there was no
OL,8,Fmedical evidence to support the
OL,9,Fdiagnoses. It found test results
OL,10,Fshowed he did not have the blood
OL,11,Fcancer and that no testing had been
OL,12,Fcarried out to confirm the genetic
OL,13,Fcondition.
OL,15,FThe investigation also found there was
OL,16,Fno evidence the diagnoses had been
OL,17,Fdiscussed with other clinicians or at
OL,18,Fa multidisciplinary panel.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1780729501
OL,3,C'Seven years stolen': Father
OL,4,Cmisdiagnosed with terminal cancer
OL,6,FGeorge Eliot Hospital NHS Trust has
OL,7,Fadmitted a breach of duty and accepted
OL,8,Fthat, had appropriate care been
OL,9,Fprovided, Mr Pearson would likely have
OL,10,Favoided 42 procedures carried out
OL,11,Fbetween 2017 and 2025.
OL,13,FThe trust has since apologised.
OL,15,FMr Pearson welcomed the admission but
OL,16,Fsaid more needed to be done to prevent
OL,17,Fsimilar cases.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1780729501
OL,3,C'Seven years stolen': Father
OL,4,Cmisdiagnosed with terminal cancer
OL,6,FHe said: "I think procedures have got
OL,7,Fto be checked and double checked,"
OL,8,Fbefore adding: "We all love the NHS
OL,9,Fand on the whole do a good job, but I
OL,10,Fthink someone can't go through what
OL,11,FI've gone through."
OL,13,F"They've got to have procedures in
OL,14,Fplace where they double-check it,
OL,15,Fespecially telling someone they've got
OL,16,Fcancer."
OL,18,F"That's an horrific thing. To get it
OL,19,Fwrong is even worse."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1780729501
OL,3,C'Seven years stolen': Father
OL,4,Cmisdiagnosed with terminal cancer
OL,6,FMr Pearson has instructed medical
OL,7,Fnegligence lawyers and is seeking
OL,8,Fsupport to help him deal with the
OL,9,Fpsychological impact of the
OL,10,Fmisdiagnosis.
OL,12,F"I had no reason to dispute anything
OL,13,Fthat I was told and put my trust in
OL,14,Fthe doctors," he said.
OL,16,F"I'm still struggling to come to terms
OL,17,Fwith the fact it was all a mistake.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1780729501
OL,3,C'Seven years stolen': Father
OL,4,Cmisdiagnosed with terminal cancer
OL,6,F"I want to share my story to raise
OL,7,Fawareness in the hope that something
OL,8,Fis done to improve care standards. I
OL,9,Fdon't want anyone else to go through
OL,10,Fwhat I've been through."
OL,12,FDr Naj Rashid, Chief Medical Officer
OL,13,Ffor George Eliot Hospital NHS Trust,
OL,14,Fsaid: "I would like to offer our
OL,15,Fsincere apologies to Mr Pearson for
OL,16,Fthe failings in the care he received
OL,17,Ffrom us.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1780729501
OL,3,C'Seven years stolen': Father
OL,4,Cmisdiagnosed with terminal cancer
OL,6,F"Mr Pearson's care had undoubtedly
OL,7,Ffallen below our usually high
OL,8,Fstandards and caused significant
OL,9,Fdistress to him."
OL,11,FHe adds, "We are working with him to
OL,12,Fensure he has our full support going
OL,13,Fforward.
OL,15,F"The Trust has carried out a thorough
OL,16,Finvestigation into what went wrong and
OL,17,Fhave put in place actions to address
OL,18,Fissues identified to ensure this is
OL,19,Fnot able to happen again."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
